1.0.name: wordpress/alex-wrong-password
1.0.description: When someone gets a password wrong or uses the forgotten password form on your site, the administrator is emailed with the details that were entered. The best way to get fast support is by posting your question in a comment at http://anthony.strangebutfunny.net/my-plugins/wrong-password/
